{{tsl|en|Ho-Sung Pak|何松柏}}扮演[[白蓮教|白蓮教]]成员{{tsl|en|Liu Kang|刘康}}，他代表[[少林寺|少林寺]]参与比赛；伊丽莎白·马莱基（Elizabeth Malecki）扮演特种部队（Special Forces）特工{{tsl|en|Sonya Blade|刀鋒索尼婭}}，她在追踪黑龙（Black Dragon）组织头号罪犯的过程中误入比赛；理查德·迪维齐奥（Richard Divizio）扮演{{tsl|en|Kano (Mortal Kombat)|加納 (真人快打)|加納}}；{{tsl|en|Carlos Pesina|卡洛斯·佩西纳}}扮演雷公{{tsl|en|Raiden (Mortal Kombat)|雷電 (真人快打)|雷电}}（MS-DOS和家用机版为“Rayden”），他以凡人的身份参加比赛；好莱坞电影巨星{{tsl|en|Johnny Cage|约翰尼·凯奇}}由佩西纳的哥哥{{tsl|en|Daniel Pesina|丹尼尔·佩斯纳|丹尼尔}}扮演；丹尼尔还扮演了不死的蝎子{{tsl|en|Scorpion (Mortal Kombat)|魔蠍 (真人快打)|魔蠍}}，一位在比赛前遇害的忍者。忍者后来重生，踏上了复仇之路；谋杀魔蝎的{{tsl|en|Sub-Zero (Mortal Kombat)|絕對零度 (真人快打)|絕對零度}}是林鬼杀手帮成员，有制冰的能力。魔蝎和绝对零度穿着同样的衣服，但颜色不同，前者是黄色，后者是蓝色，而这就是游戏最为著名的{{tsl|en|palette swap|色調變換}}特色，后续的新角色也以这种方式出现<ref name=oh/>。

游戏的小BOSS是绍康派的四臂战士{{tsl|en|Goro (Mortal Kombat)|戈洛}}，他是人与龙的化身，力量比其他角色都要强大，不受投技影响。戈洛的精灵画面由柯特·基亚雷利（Curt Chiarelli）以[[定格动画|定格动画]]模式创建。游戏大BOSS{{tsl|en|Shang Tsung|尚宗}}是巫师，在战斗过程中可以变身为任何一个角色。该角色由埃里克·金凯德（Eric Kincade）和何松柏两位演员扮演，但只有后者被列入制作名单。

在深坑（Pit）关比赛的时候，玩家和隐藏角色{{le|蜥蝪人 (真人快打)|Reptile (Mortal Kombat)|蜥蝪人}}一战。蜥蜴人是魔蝎和绝对零度的绿色版，特定情况下会使用两者的招式<ref>{{cite web |last1=Carter |first1=Chip |last2=Carter |first2=Jonathan |title=They are just dying to talk about Mortal Kombat |url=https://www.tampabay.com/archive/1994/02/07/they-are-just-dying-to-talk-about-mortal-kombat/ |website=Tampa Bay Times |accessdate=2022-06-15 |date=1994-02-07 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615075858/https://www.tampabay.com/archive/1994/02/07/they-are-just-dying-to-talk-about-mortal-kombat/ }}</ref>。戈洛、尚宗和蜥蜴人是非玩家角色。庭院（Courtyard）关的蒙面侍卫（The Masked Guard）由游戏开发人员约翰·沃格尔（John Vogel）扮演<ref>{{cite web |title=Mortal Kombat: Shaolin Monks PlayStation 2 Gameplay - Legends of Kombat: Goro, Baraka, and Masked Guard |url=http://ps2.ign.com/dor/objects/709115/mortal-kombat-shaolin-monks/videos/mkshaolin_090805_doc_01.html |website=IGN |access-date=2010-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090702101210/http://ps2.ign.com/dor/objects/709115/mortal-kombat-shaolin-monks/videos/mkshaolin_090805_doc_01.html |archive-date=2009-07-02 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

== 开发 ==
据游戏制作人{{tsl|en|Ed Boon|艾德·波恩}}和{{tsl|en|John Tobias|约翰·托比亚斯}}透露，[[Midway|Midway]]要求开发一款格斗类游戏，“一年内发行”，他们认为公司这是跟[[卡普空|卡普空]]炙手可热的《[[街頭霸王II_－世界勇士－|街頭霸王II －世界勇士－]]》对撼<ref name="1994 interview"/>。托比亚斯表示，他和波恩设想的游戏跟[[Data_East|Data East]]的《{{tsl|en|Karate Champ|空手道冠军}}》相像，但数字角色的数量比以往都要多，而《街头霸王II》能让他们说服管理层同意这个想法<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://index.html/|title=John Tobias, Mortal Kombat co-creator {{!}} Interview {{!}} The Gameological Society|language=en|access-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080505195009/http://index.html/|archive-date=2008-05-05|url-status=dead}}</ref>。波恩表示开发团队最初只有四个人，自己是程序员，约翰·托比亚斯和约翰·沃格尔做美工，{{tsl|en|Dan Forden|丹·福登}}负责音效<ref name="mortalkombatint">{{cite magazine | url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/news_060707_mortal.html | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071023152817/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/news_060707_mortal.html | archive-date=2007-10-23 | title=Mortal Kombat: Ed Boon Interview | magazine=Official Nintendo Magazine | access-date=2009-08-02}}</ref>。开发预算约为100万美元<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/86822190/|title=Bloody arcade smash started as a rush job|newspaper=The Kansas City Star|date=1995-11-06|accessdate=2021-08-24|via=Newspapers.com|archive-date=2022-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615074608/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/86822190/the-kansas-city-star/}}</ref>。

理查德·迪维齐奥和丹尼尔·佩斯纳回忆，一开始托比亚斯、迪维齐奥与丹尼尔和卡洛斯·佩斯纳兄弟想打造一款忍者主题的游戏，但被个主意被Midway的管理层一致否决<ref name=oh>{{cite web|url=https://melmagazine.com/en-us/story/an-oral-history-of-mortal-kombat|title=An Oral History of 'Mortal Kombat'|date=2018-11-26|website=MEL Magazine|access-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127144229/https://melmagazine.com/en-us/story/an-oral-history-of-mortal-kombat|archive-date=2018-11-27|url-status=dead}}</ref>。相反，Midway想给即将上映的电影《[[再造战士|再造战士]]》做一款动作游戏，由动作巨星[[尚格云顿|尚格云顿]]出演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://g4tv.com/gamemakers/episodes/3446/Mortal-Kombat.html |title=Video Games, Game Reviews & News |publisher=G4tv.com |date=2004-02-09 |access-date=2012-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806163531/http://www.g4tv.com/gamemakers/episodes/3446/Mortal-Kombat.html |archive-date=2011-08-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref>，但尚格云顿已经和另一家游戏公司进行谈判，但那家公司最终没有推出游戏。之后迪维齐奥说服托比亚斯回归原本的计划<ref name=oh/>，而尚格云顿在游戏中被恶搞成约翰尼·凯奇的角色（凯奇英文名的首字母就是JC）。凯奇是好莱坞电影巨星，非常自恋。游戏中，凯奇对对手腹股沟劈拳的动作参考了《[[拳霸天下|拳霸天下]]》<ref>{{cite web|title=Bloodsport Fight #2 at 6:50 |website = YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BtcrFCfoyxo |access-date=2009-07-20 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519093855/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BtcrFCfoyxo |archive-date=2014-05-19 }}</ref>。托比亚斯表示游戏也参考了亚洲的功夫电影<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1"/>。

波恩后来表示：“自打一开始，我们就想做跟其他格斗游戏不同的东西，其中一个就是加入疯狂的招式，譬如喷火及所有魔法招式<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=162494|title=Ed Boon talks Mortal Kombat|last=Bishop|first=Stuart|date=2007-04-23|magazine=Computer and Video Games|access-date=2009-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090721105756/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=162494|archive-date=2009-07-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。”托比亚斯表示，游戏中的暴力内容并不在最初的计划中，是后来在开发过程中实施的<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_z7bAEMVRMU |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105181933/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_z7bAEMVRMU |archive-date=2019-01-05 |url-status=dead|title=Mortal Kombat II 25th Anniversary Interview w/ John Tobias and Matt Campy|last=Dude Nobody Cares|via=YouTube}}</ref>。至于必杀技的概念则衍生自早期格斗游戏的“眩晕”机制，波恩说他讨厌“眩晕”机制，但肆意打击“眩晕”对手的快感的确很爽。波恩和托比亚斯决定抵消“眩晕”机制给人带来的不良观感，把这个机制放在游戏结束，也就是胜负已分的时候<ref>{{cite magazine|title=Mortal's Master: Programmer Ed Boon|magazine=GamePro|issue=86|publisher=International Data Group|date=November 1995|pages=38–40}}</ref>。在早期版本中，中路拳击及踢技需要用两个以上的按键释放<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eventhubs.com/news/2012/nov/07/john-tobias-if-i-could-go-back-and-redo-kabal-and-stryker-i-would-i-dont-know-if-id-design-them-differently-or-just-come-new-character/|title=John Tobias: 'If I could go back and redo Kabal and Stryker I would, I don't know if I'd design them differently or just come up with new characters'|date=2012-11-07|website=EventHubs|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304123826/http://www.eventhubs.com/news/2012/nov/07/john-tobias-if-i-could-go-back-and-redo-kabal-and-stryker-i-would-i-dont-know-if-id-design-them-differently-or-just-come-new-character/|archive-date=2016-03-04|url-status=live|access-date=2018-12-24}}</ref>。

游戏开发工作于1991年启动，1992年结束，历时10个月，其中测试版在开发阶段中途有限发行<ref name="1994 interview">{{cite news|first=Stephen|last=Lynch|title=They program the best incarnations of games they played as kids|url=https://www.deseret.com/1994/4/19/19105936/they-program-the-best-incarnations-of-games-they-played-as-kids|work=Deseret News|date=1994-04-19|page=2|accessdate=2022-06-14|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413220603/https://www.deseret.com/1994/4/19/19105936/they-program-the-best-incarnations-of-games-they-played-as-kids}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first= David |last= Craddock |title= The Rogues Gallery: Controversial Video Games |date= 2005-09-29 |url= http://www.shacknews.com/featuredarticle.x?id=23 |publisher= Shacknews |access-date= 2009-09-08 |url-status= dead |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20081210010820/http://www.shacknews.com/featuredarticle.x?id=23 |archive-date= 2008-12-10 }}</ref>。作为游戏的[[游戏演示|演示版]]，内测版只有六位男性角色<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/286864/Mortal_Kombat_dev_Ed_Boon_recalls_the_uppercut_that_started_it_all.php|title=Mortal Kombat dev Ed Boon recalls the uppercut that started it all|last=Wawro|first=Alex|website=www.gamasutra.com|date=2016-12-02|language=en|access-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225031128/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/286864/Mortal_Kombat_dev_Ed_Boon_recalls_the_uppercut_that_started_it_all.php|archive-date=2018-12-25|url-status=live}}</ref>，但在Midway公司内部相当受欢迎。开发团队于是投入时间打磨角色，将索尼娅加入到角色名单<ref name=":0" />。游戏角色画面是托比亚斯用自己的{{tsl|en|Hi-8|Hi-8}}摄影机录制的<ref>{{cite magazine|title=The Game Makers: The Artists|magazine=GamePro|issue=88 |publisher=International Data Group|date=January 1996|page=35}}</ref>。最终的街机版采用8-Bit图像，每个角色采用64色，动画帧数约为300帧<ref>Interview with Gary Liddon, ''Mega'', issue 10, page 36, Future Publishing, July 1993</ref>。

在给游戏取名的时候，开发团队犯了难。波恩表示整个团队半年来都想不到一个大家满意的名字。有些人提出了《{{tsl|en|Kumite|组手}}》（''Kumite''）、《龙击》（''Dragon Attack''）、《死亡气息》（''Death Blow''）、《致命格斗》（''Fatality''）的名字，直至有一天波恩办公室的白板出现了“Combat”（打斗）这个词。后来这个词的“C”被改成“K”，波恩说这样看上去“相当疯狂”<ref>{{cite magazine |title= Episode 123 of KOXM |url= http://dl.oxmonline.com/oxmp_123_20080710.mp3 |date= July 2008 |magazine= Official Xbox Magazine |access-date= 2009-10-21 |url-status= dead |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110715030437/http://dl.oxmonline.com/oxmp_123_20080710.mp3 |archive-date= 2011-07-15 }}</ref>。弹珠台设计师{{tsl|en|Steve Ritchie (pinball designer)|史蒂夫·里奇}}坐在波恩办公室里看到这个词，跟伯恩说“不如就叫《Mortal Kombat》吧”，伯恩也觉得“很炸”。然而托比亚斯对此事的回忆有出入，说名字是在商标设计过程中出现的，当时大家都喜欢叫《Mortal Combat》，但法律不允许<ref name=":1" />。从那个时候起，整个系列就频繁用“K”取代“C”，而K是C的[[清軟腭塞音|重音]]。

== 发行 ==
[[File:PAX_South_2015_-_Mortal_Kombat_arcade_(16165005248).jpg|thumb]]》机台亮相2015年[[PAX游戏展|PAX游戏展]]。]]

尽管从未按照惯例进行本地化，游戏还是于1992年由[[太东|太东]]在日本正式发行，为进口自北美的版本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.taito.co.jp/game_history/index.html|title=Taito Game History|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030621100427/http://www.taito.co.jp/game_history/index.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=2003-06-21|date=2003-06-21}}</ref>。家用机版则由{{le|赞誉娱乐|Acclaim Entertainment}}发行，是当年数一数二的家用及游戏。大量电视广告显示游戏会1993年9月13日在[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]、[[Mega_Drive|Genesis]]、[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]和[[Game_Gear|Game Gear]]四个家用级平台发行，当天被称为“快打星期一”<ref>{{cite magazine|title=Fightin' Words|magazine=GamePro|issue=58|publisher=International Data Group|date=May 1994|pages=12–13}}</ref>。同人漫画书《{{tsl|en|Mortal Kombat (comics)#Mortal Kombat Collector's Edition|真人快打典藏版}}》于同年出版，由托比亚斯创作，以[[邮购|邮购]]方式发售。漫画以丰富的细节展现游戏的背景故事，在街机版的演示模式中有广告出现。漫画后来开放全美购买，美国以外地区则较难买到。该书后来收录于游戏《真人快打：致命同盟》，以附加内容的形式出现。

{{tsl|en|Mortal Kombat: The Album|真人快打 (专辑)|同名配乐专辑}}由{{tsl|en|The Immortals (band)|不死者乐队}}制作，采用[[Techno|Techno]]风格，1994年5月发行。专辑收录游戏两大主题音乐《Techno Syndrome》和《Hypnotic House》，以及每个主角的主题音乐。《Techno Syndrome》之后出现在[[魔宮帝國_(電影)|1995年改编电影]]的原声带中，融入了游戏电视广告中知名的“Mortal Kombat！”口号<ref>{{cite web|url=http://immortals.pragakhan.com/biography.html|title=The Immortals - Biography|website=immortals.pragakhan.com|access-date=2018-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100626042925/http://immortals.pragakhan.com/biography.html|archive-date=2010-06-26|url-status=dead}}</ref>。游戏第一部的同人小说由{{tsl|en|Jeff Rovin|杰夫·罗文}}创作，1995年6月配合电影上市。另有角色活动手办推出。

===家用机版===
[[File:MK1_SNES_vs_MD.png|thumb]]
四款官方移植版于1993年以“快打星期一”（Mortal Monday）的活动登陆北美，其中主机版登陆[[超级任天堂|超级任天堂]]和[[Mega_Drive|世嘉Genesis]]，便携版登陆[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]和[[Game_Gear|Game Gear]]。超级任天堂版尽管在还原街机版色彩和音效的表现上比Genesis优秀，但控制不太精准，而且血迹在任天堂“合家欢”政策影响下变成了汗水，必杀技也大多变成暴力元素较少的“终结技”<ref name="archive.gamespy.com">{{cite web |url=http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/june03/dumbestmoments/readers/index4.shtml |title=Gamespy's The 25 Dumbest Moments in Gaming |publisher=Archive.gamespy.com |access-date=2012-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040818132132/http://archive.gamespy.com/articles/june03/dumbestmoments/readers/index4.shtml |archive-date=2004-08-18 |url-status=live }}</ref>。所谓的汗水其实是应任天堂的审查决定改变了颜色，实机操作时可插入{{tsl|en|Game Genie|游戏精灵}}作弊卡带，输入代码“BDB4-DD07”调成原来的红色。在Genesis版中，血和原版的必杀技可用[[电子游戏作弊|作弊码]]ABACABB调出<ref>{{cite web |first= Travis |last= Fahs |title= IGN Presents the History of Mortal Kombat |date= 2008-10-13 |url= http://retro.ign.com/articles/919/919357p2.html |website= IGN |access-date= 2009-12-06 |url-status= dead |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100628214138/http://retro.ign.com/articles/919/919357p2.html |archive-date= 2010-06-28 }}</ref>，这个码致敬了[[創世紀樂團|創世紀樂團]]的专辑《{{tsl|en|Abacab|Abacab}}》，乐队名字恰好和主机的名字同名。Genesis被[[电子游戏分级委员会|电子游戏分级委员会]]评为MA-13级，即适合13岁或以上人士游玩。

Game Boy版内容较主机版少，按键反应滞后，按键布局有限，约翰尼·凯奇、蜥蜴人及血腥的必杀技被省略。不过玩家可以用作弊码扮演戈洛<ref>{{cite web|title=Mortal Kombat Review|url=http://retro.nintendolife.com/reviews/2010/08/mortal_kombat_retro|date=2010-08-05|access-date=2010-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100808025806/http://retro.nintendolife.com/reviews/2010/08/mortal_kombat_retro|archive-date=2010-08-08|url-status=live}}</ref>。原本是玩家角色的约翰尼·凯奇被删除，但其角色数据仍有留存<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD3C-BUoOEs |title=Johnny Cage in Gameboy Mortal Kombat |publisher=YouTube |date=2009-06-24 |access-date=2012-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140914193044/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD3C-BUoOEs |archive-date=2014-09-14 |url-status=live }}</ref>。Game Gear版本与Game Boy类似，但色彩有所改进，游戏节奏更快，按键反应更紧凑。和16色版本相比，游戏内容遭到审查，但可以通过作弊码2、1、2、下、上调出，唯独缺少加納和蜥蜴人。根据Game Gear版移植的[[世嘉Master_System|世嘉Master System]]版1994年初面向PAL区发行。赞誉娱乐的弗林·里格斯（Phylene Riggs）表示，当时[[红白机|红白机]]版本也计划推出，但在进入编程阶段前就被腰斩<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://archive.org/details/Electronic_Gaming_Monthly_51/page/n25|title=Where's Mortal Kombat For...|magazine=Electronic Gaming Monthly|issue=51|publisher=EGM Media, LLC|date=October 1993|page=26}}</ref>。

[[MS-DOS|MS-DOS]]移植版于1993年底发行。这个版本最能还原街机版的效果，无论是图像上还是玩法上。游戏最初以软盘发行，随后以CD-ROM再版发行，后者增加了街机原版的音乐及音效。[[Amiga|Amiga]]版于1994年初发行，仅限欧洲，图形以Genesis版为蓝本，控制仅用一个或两个按键，配乐采用最小限度，由{{tsl|en|Allister Brimble|阿利斯特·布里布尔}}编排。

[[Mega-CD|Sega CD]]版的片头采用《快打星期一》的广告。这个版本不需要作弊码就可以享受到原版的内容，因而被评为MA-17级。这个版本尽管技术表现比超级任天堂差，而且设有加载时间，但更忠实于街机版的玩法。该版附有[[數位音樂光碟|CD-DA]]原声带，音轨直接取自街机版，但部分关卡的配乐出错，譬如庭院关播放了深坑关的音乐。游戏还附录了游戏音乐的重混版，其中一个版本在之后的改编电影中出现。然而这个版本不兼容Sega CD的1.1版。赞誉娱乐将寄到他们{{tsl|en|Oyster Bay (hamlet), New York|牡蛎湾 (纽约)|牡蛎湾}}总部的不兼容光碟更换成可用的版本<ref>{{cite magazine|title=Buyers Beware|magazine=GamePro|issue=62|publisher=International Data Group|date=September 1994|page=156}}</ref>。

日本版《{{nihongo|真人快打 神拳降临传奇|モータルコンバット 神拳降臨伝説|Mōtaru Konbatto: Shinken Kōrin Densetsu}}》登陆Game Gear、[[超級任天堂|Super Famicom]]、Game Boy和[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive]] <ref>{{cite web |title=Mortal Kombat: Shinken Kourin Densetsu (JP, 05/27/94) |url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/genesis/563332-mortal-kombat/images/box-2952 |access-date=2009-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102031614/http://www.gamefaqs.com/genesis/563332-mortal-kombat/images/box-2952 |archive-date=2012-11-02 |url-status=live }}</ref>，《{{nihongo|真人快打 神拳降临传奇 完全版|モータルコンバット 神拳降臨伝説 完全版|Mōtaru Konbatto: Shinken Kōrin Densetsu - Kanzenhan}}》登陆[[Mega-CD|Mega-CD]]，内容与原版无异。

源计划在[[雅达利Jaguar|雅达利Jaguar]]平台发行的移植版由{{tsl|en|Acclaim Studios Austin|赞誉奥斯汀工作室|鬣蜥娱乐}}开发<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://archive.org/stream/Edge_UK_005#page/n9|title=News - Jaguar bares its claws - Complete Atari Jaguar thirdparty release schedule|magazine=Edge|issue=5|publisher=Future plc|date=February 1994|pages=10–11}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.stformat.com/stf56/pages_nx1500/stf56_048.jpg|title=News - Update - Around the corner... - Expected Release Dates|magazine=ST Format|issue=56|publisher=Future plc|date=March 1994|page=48|access-date=2018-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719133302/http://stformat.com/stf56/pages_nx1500/stf56_048.jpg|archive-date=2016-07-19|url-status=live}}</ref>，但从未发行<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.atarimania.com/mags/hi_res/atari-st-format-issue-059_57.jpg|title=Update - Games News - Atari ooze confidence at ECTS - Jaguar Developers|magazine=ST Format|issue=59|publisher=Future plc|date=June 1994|pages=56–57|access-date=2018-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927010613/http://www.atarimania.com/mags/hi_res/atari-st-format-issue-059_57.jpg|archive-date=2018-09-27|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://retrocdn.net/index.php?title=File%3AHyper_AU_007.pdf&page=9|title=News - Jaguar Technology for MK III|magazine=Hyper|publisher=Next Media Pty Ltd|issue=7|date=June 1994|page=9|access-date=2018-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912092025/https://retrocdn.net/index.php?title=File%3AHyper_AU_007.pdf&page=9|archive-date=2018-09-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2004年，游戏收录至{{tsl|en|Backbone Entertainment|骨干娱乐|数字日食}}开发、{{tsl|en|Jakks Pacific|杰克仕太平洋}}发行的“即插即玩电视游戏”（''Plug It in & Play TV Games''）系列。这个版本直接用了克里斯·伯克（Chris Burke）当初为街机版写的代码，而伯克也因此成为该版本的唯一一位程序员。由于杰克仕太平洋采用的处理器单元并不常见，存在较大的机能限制，游戏背景为静态画面，没有视差滚动。这个版本分别有原版和净化版，评级分别为T级和M级<ref>{{cite web |title=''Mortal Kombat'' for Jakks TV Games |url=http://cyberabi.ipower.com/Gallery/JakksMK/index.html |website=CYBERABI |accessdate=2010-08-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713053138/http://cyberabi.ipower.com/Gallery/JakksMK/index.html |archivedate=2011-07-13}}</ref>。同样在2004年，《{{le|真人快打6|Mortal Kombat: Deception}}》登陆[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]和初代[[Xbox_(遊戲機)|Xbox]]，两个版本均以附加内容形式收录原本游戏，[[仿真器|模拟]]了街机原版的代码。尽管开发商宣扬这个模拟“如街机版完美”，它还是有音效及玩法上的问题<ref name="MK Deception Limited Edition">{{cite web |author=Jeremy Dunham |url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/535/535211p1.html |title=MK Deception Limited Edition – PlayStation 2 News at IGN |date=2004-08-02 |publisher=Ps2.ign.com |access-date=2012-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225074504/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/535/535211p1.html |archive-date=2012-02-25 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

游戏收录于2005年发行的合辑《{{tsl|en|Midway Arcade Treasures: Extended Play|Midway街机宝藏}}》。和《真人快打6》的版本一样，这个版本也存在声音问题。2011年8月31日，[[華納兄弟互動娛樂|華納兄弟互動娛樂]]发行《{{tsl|en|Mortal Kombat Arcade Kollection|真人快打街机合集}}》，收录《真人快打》、《[[真人快打II|真人快打II]]》和《{{tsl|en|Ultimate Mortal Kombat 3|真人快打3}}》，面向[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]发行。

== 反响 ==
在美国，《Replay》杂志称《真人快打》是1992年9月第二吸金的直立式{{tsl|en|arcade cabinet|街机台}}<ref>{{cite magazine|title=The Player's Choice - Top Games Now in Operation, Based on Earnings-Opinion Poll of Operators: Best Upright Videos|magazine=RePlay|volume=17|issue=12|publisher=RePlay Publishing, Inc.|date=September 1992|page=4}}</ref>。1992年10月到11月<ref>{{cite magazine |title=RePlay: The Players' Choice |magazine=RePlay |date=October 1992 |volume=18 |issue=1 |page=4 |url=https://archive.org/details/re-play-volume-18-issue-no.-1-october-1992-600dpi/RePlay%20-%20Volume%2018%2C%20Issue%20No.%201%20-%20October%201992/page/4}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |title=RePlay: The Players' Choice |magazine=RePlay |date=November 1992 |volume=18 |issue=2 |page=4 |url=https://archive.org/details/re-play-volume-18-issue-no.-2-november-1992-600DPI/RePlay%20-%20Volume%2018%2C%20Issue%20No.%202%20-%20November%201992/page/4/mode/1up}}</ref>、1993年2月到3月<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Top Coin-Ops: Feb. 1993 |magazine=Electronic Games |date=1993-03-16 |volume=1 |issue=7 (April 1993) |page=12 |url=https://archive.org/details/Electronic-Games-1993-04/page/n11}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |title=Top Coin-Ops of March 1993 |magazine=Electronic Games |date=April 1993 |volume=1 |issue=8 (May 1993) |page=14 |url=https://archive.org/details/Electronic-Games-1993-05/page/n13}}</ref>、1993年11月<ref>{{cite magazine |title=RePlay: The Players' Choice |magazine=RePlay |date=November 1993 |volume=19 |issue=2 |page=10 |url=https://archive.org/details/re-play-volume-19-issue-no.-2-november-1993/RePlay%20-%20Volume%2019%2C%20Issue%20No.%202%20-%20November%201993/page/n9/mode/1up}}</ref>，游戏三度位列《Replay》杂志街机台榜单榜首。除此之外，游戏还位列1992年12月《{{tsl|en|Play Meter|Play Meter}}》杂志街机榜榜首<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Equipment Poll |magazine=Play Meter |date=December 1992 |volume=18 |issue=13 |pages=8–9 |url=https://archive.org/details/play-meter-volume-18-number-13-december-1992-600DPI/Play%20Meter%20-%20Volume%2018%2C%20Number%2013%20-%20December%201992%20%28Compressed%29/page/8/mode/2up}}</ref>。另据《Replay》杂志，1993年夏季，游戏成为第二吸金的街机游戏，仅次于《{{tsl|en|NBA Jam (1993 video game)|NBA大灌篮}}》<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Game Center Poll: Top Games |magazine=RePlay |date=November 1993 |volume=19 |issue=2 |page=142 |url=https://archive.org/details/re-play-volume-19-issue-no.-2-november-1993/RePlay%20-%20Volume%2019%2C%20Issue%20No.%202%20-%20November%201993/page/142}}</ref>。游戏和《NBA大灌篮》是1993年美国最为吸金的[[1993年电子游戏界|街机游戏]] ，收益越吵同年电影《[[侏罗纪公园|侏罗纪公园]]》{{US$|300,000,000|long=no|1993|round=-7}}<ref>{{cite news |last1=McKanic |first1=Patricia Ann |title=Video values: It's a whole new game for the industry |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=49wvAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dfwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4448,1185138 |access-date=2021-02-17 |work=Lakeland Ledger |date=1994-03-24 |archive-date=2022-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220519223529/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=49wvAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dfwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4448%2C1185138 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=McKanic |first1=Patricia Ann |title=Games more complex, but also more violent |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1842&dat=19940403&id=8UoeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DccEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1756,337084 |access-date=2021-02-17 |work=Times Daily |date=1994-04-03 |archive-date=2022-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220519223529/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1842&dat=19940403&id=8UoeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DccEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1756%2C337084 }}</ref>。[[1994年电子游戏界|1994年6月]]，游戏位列Sega CD销量榜榜首<ref name="EGMAug1994">{{cite magazine|date=August 1994|title=EGM's Hot Top Tens|url=https://retrocdn.net/images/6/66/EGM_US_061.pdf|magazine=Electronic Gaming Monthly|pages=42|access-date=2022-06-14|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831090937/https://retrocdn.net/images/6/66/EGM_US_061.pdf}}</ref>。

1993年11月，赞誉娱乐宣布登陆超级任天堂、Genesis、Game Boy和Game Gear四大平台的游戏家用机版销量突破300万份<ref>{{cite magazine|title=Mortal Marketing|date=February 1994|magazine=GamePro|publisher=International Data Group|issue=65|page=187}}</ref>，此时上市才不到三周<ref>{{cite book |last1=Ali |first1=Reyan |title=NBA Jam |date=2019-10-22 |publisher=Boss Fight Books |isbn=978-1-940535-20-3 |page=138 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9zC-DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA138 |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2021-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021185354/https://books.google.com/books?id=9zC-DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA138 }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |title=Mortal Kombat kicks butt |magazine=Mega Zone |date=1994-01-26 |issue=36 (February 1994) |page=11 |url=https://archive.org/details/megazoneau36/page/n10}}</ref>。在美国，游戏位列1994年1月世嘉Genesis及超级任天堂游戏销量榜榜首<ref name="EGMMar1994">{{cite magazine|date=March 1994|title=EGM Hot Top Tens|url=https://retrocdn.net/images/a/ae/EGM_US_056.pdf|magazine=Electronic Gaming Monthly|pages=48|access-date=2022-06-14|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831085221/https://retrocdn.net/images/a/ae/EGM_US_056.pdf}}</ref>。而在英国，游戏成为1993年10月最畅销的家用及游戏<ref name="Counsell">{{cite news |last1=Counsell |first1=Gail |title=Sega slashes profit forecast: Video game group says strength of yen will hit earnings |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/sega-slashes-profit-forecast-video-game-group-says-strength-of-yen-will-hit-earnings-gail-counsell-reports-1503374.html |access-date=2021-09-15 |work=The Independent |date=1993-11-10 |archive-date=2022-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220604075446/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/sega-slashes-profit-forecast-video-game-group-says-strength-of-yen-will-hit-earnings-gail-counsell-reports-1503374.html }}</ref>、1994年5月到8月最畅销的世嘉Master System游戏<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://retrocdn.net/images/4/45/CVG_UK_152.pdf |title=Chart Attack with HMV |magazine=Computer & Video Games |publisher=Future plc |issue=152 (July 1994) |date=1994-06-15 |pages=126–128 |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2022-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220116134810/https://retrocdn.net/images/4/45/CVG_UK_152.pdf }}</ref><ref name="CVGJuneChart">{{cite magazine |url=https://retrocdn.net/images/6/61/CVG_UK_153.pdf |title=Chart Attack with HMV |magazine=Computer & Video Games |publisher=Future plc |issue=153 (August 1994) |date=1994-07-15 |pages=126–128 |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511040638/https://retrocdn.net/images/6/61/CVG_UK_153.pdf }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://retrocdn.net/images/8/8c/CVG_UK_154.pdf |title=Chart Attack with HMV |magazine=Computer & Video Games |publisher=Future plc |issue=154 (September 1994) |date=1994-08-15 |pages=112–113 |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2022-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220601172206/https://retrocdn.net/images/8/8c/CVG_UK_154.pdf }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://retrocdn.net/images/1/14/CVG_UK_155.pdf |title=Chart Attack with HMV |magazine=Computer & Video Games |publisher=Future plc |issue=155 (October 1994) |date=1994-09-15 |pages=128–129 |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2019-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818192723/https://retrocdn.net/images/1/14/CVG_UK_155.pdf }}</ref>，1994年6月最畅销的Mega CD游戏<ref name="CVGJuneChart"/>。

到1994年7月，游戏主机版卡带销量突破600万份<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Gillen|first=Marilyn A.|date=1994-07-30|title=The Enter*Active File: Acclaim Readies 'Kombat' Battle|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aQgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA104|magazine=Billboard|volume=106|issue=31|page=104|issn=0006-2510|access-date=2022-06-14|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412093308/https://books.google.com/books?id=aQgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA104}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Schuyler |first1=Nina |title=The Business of Multimedia |date=1995 |publisher=Allworth Press |isbn=978-1-880559-31-4 |page=47 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=561vFjhZdHoC |quote=The original version sold more than 6 million since its introduction in September 1993. |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411225622/https://books.google.com/books?id=561vFjhZdHoC }}</ref>，收益达到{{US$|300,000,000|long=no|1993|round=-7}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/85254724/|title=Game: Mortal Kombat II sells|newspaper=The Central New Jersey Home News|page=5|date=1994-09-12|accessdate=2021-08-24|via=Newspapers.com|archive-date=2021-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107100149/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/85254724/the-central-new-jersey-home-news/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Strauss |first1=Neil |title=Mortal Kombat fans get their kicks at tour |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/9382746/mortalkombatfansgettheirkicksatto/ |access-date=2021-02-17 |work=The Desert Sun |date=1995-09-20 |pages=13 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615074607/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/9382746/mortalkombatfansgettheirkicksatto/ }}</ref>。至2000年，全平台卡带全球销量突破650万，其中Genesis版占大部分<ref>{{cite book |last1=Kent |first1=Steven L. |title=The First Quarter: A 25-year History of Video Games |date=2000 |publisher=BWD Press |isbn=978-0-9704755-0-3 |page=372 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ny-CAAAAMAAJ |quote=Acclaim sold approximately 6.5 million ''Mortal Kombat'' cartridges. The Genesis version, which included the original arcade fatality moves, outsold the edited-down Super NES version by nearly three-to-one |access-date=2022-06-14 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511174339/https://books.google.com/books?id=ny-CAAAAMAAJ }}</ref>。截至2002年，街机原版销量达2.4万份，收益突破5.7亿美元。加上衍生的影视作品，游戏总营销突破15亿美元<ref>{{cite news |last1=Horwitz |first1=Jeremy |title=Mortal Apathy? |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/07/08/technology/08MIDW.html |access-date=2021-02-15 |work=The New York Times |date=2002-07-08 |url-access=subscription |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003002950/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/07/08/business/technology-mortal-apathy.html?pagewanted=2 |archive-date=2013-10-03 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

